# Test 13: FizzBuzz simplified
Show "FizzBuzz (1-15):".
For i from 1 to 15, do:
    Set mod15 to i modulo 15.
    Set mod3 to i modulo 3.
    Set mod5 to i modulo 5.
    If mod15 equals 0, then:
        Show "FizzBuzz".
    End if.
    If mod3 equals 0, then:
        If mod15 is not equal to 0, then:
            Show "Fizz".
        End if.
    End if.
    If mod5 equals 0, then:
        If mod15 is not equal to 0, then:
            If mod3 is not equal to 0, then:
                Show "Buzz".
            End if.
        End if.
    End if.
    If mod15 is not equal to 0, then:
        If mod3 is not equal to 0, then:
            If mod5 is not equal to 0, then:
                Show i.
            End if.
        End if.
    End if.
End for.
